<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id47db532d-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a" identifier="/us/usc/t26/s9834"><num value="9834">§ 9834.</num><heading> Enforcement</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I23" class="indent2 fontsize7">For the imposition of tax on any failure of a group health plan to meet the requirements of this chapter, see section 4980D.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id47db532e-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/110/233/tI/s103/e/1">Pub. L. 110–233, title I, § 103(e)(1)</ref>, <date date="2008-05-21">May 21, 2008</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/122/899">122 Stat. 899</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id47db532f-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id47db5330-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="id47db5331-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section applicable with respect to group health plans for plan years beginning after the date that is one year after <date date="2008-05-21">May 21, 2008</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/110/233/s103/f/2">section 103(f)(2) of Pub. L. 110–233</ref>, set out as an Effective Date of 2008 Amendment note under <ref href="/us/usc/t26/s9802">section 9802 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
